    "Food tests: testing unknown food samples for all four biological molecules",
    "Transpiration: potometer measurement at different conditions",
    "Fermentation: yeast in sugar solution producing CO2 (limewater turns milky)",
    "Reflex testing: knee-jerk reflex and pupil light reflex",
    "Osmosis modelling: dialysis tubing as artificial kidney"
  ]
